<br>
Not sure how POP would affect this mentality, cos the stats would be capped at 305 instead. We'll wait and see.<br>
<br>
As for your items, these upgrades would be good [don't have to be now, but things you can take your time to upgrade until L58 - 6<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> :<br>
