Head: Champion's Crown / Helm of Raldukan<br>
Wrist: Silver Chitin Bracer / Bracelet of Fortitude / Bracer of Benevolence<br>
Feet: Champion's Boots<br>
Arms: Cobalt Vambraces<br>
Neck: Clattering Bone Necklace<br>
Back:<br>
[If Haste=Waist]:Cloak of the Maelstrom / Ancient Seahorse Hide Cloak<br>
[If Haste=Back]: Keep Haste item<br>
Wist:<br>
[If Haste=Back]:Axgoreth's Belt of Defense/Bloodruned Girdle/Belt of the Great Turtle<br>
[If Haste=Waist]: Keep Haste item<br>
Shoulders: Imbued Granite Spaulders/Any Dragonhide Spaulders/Barbed Dragonscale Pauldrons<br>
Finger: AC6 65HP Ring<br>
Ear: Vah Shir Claw Earring / Earring of the Solstice<br>
Face: Crystal Spider Eyes / Eyepatch of Plunder<br>
<br>
Don't try to upgrade everything immediately, but upgrade as you level up. Level is above all, the most important thing, as compared with Equipment, or in future, AA skills.<br>
